<br>
Loc at start of casting = (X0, Y0, Z0)<br>
Loc at end of casting = (X1, Y1, Z1)<br>
Channeling Skill = C<br>
Channeling to Movment function = f(C) <br>
<br>
successfulCast = (Sqrt((X0-X1)^2 + (Y0-Y1)^2) &lt; f(C))<br>
<br>
Yes, Z coordinates are not checked.  You can cast spells while levitating down infinite distances, as long as you don't move laterally.<br>
<br>
<br>
The problem in PvP is you cannot &quot;stand still&quot; and chain cast to kill 2 wizards faster than they can kill you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showPrevMessage?topicID=54.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showNextMessage?topicID=54.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.threadControl?topicID=54.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=54.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=54.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianstowerfrm45">User Interface<option value="themagicianstowerspells">Spells<option value="themagicianstowerequipmentandquests">Quests<option value="themagicianstowerfrm28">Equipment<